        <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:2rem;">India Gully provides bespoke research mandates for institutional investors, developers and hotel owners. Custom feasibility studies, market demand analyses, procurement cost benchmarks and regulatory due diligence packages \u2014 all built on our proprietary transaction data and network intelligence.</p>
